you have to go abroad.

225
00:23:23,802 --> 00:23:26,802
And you see your wife
one month a year.

226
00:23:27,572 --> 00:23:30,207
Why stay with one employer
for 22 months?

227
00:23:30,208 --> 00:23:32,343
You were angry
when we wanted to film?

228
00:23:32,344 --> 00:23:35,344
I was. I had slept badly.

229
00:23:37,282 --> 00:23:40,282
The bed wasn't made
and I was very tired.

230
