00:56:30,787 --> 00:56:33,787
What are you going to do?

492
00:56:34,491 --> 00:56:37,491
We're not young any more, are we?

493
00:56:40,730 --> 00:56:42,765
Will you stay here?

494
00:56:42,766 --> 00:56:45,766
Yes, we'll stay here
until we retire. And then...

495
00:56:47,904 --> 00:56:50,239
that's it.

496
00:56:50,240 --> 00:56:52,941
