497
00:56:52,942 --> 00:56:55,942
The same applies for just about
everyone here.

498
00:57:04,921 --> 00:57:07,823
I have always lived here.

499
00:57:07,824 --> 00:57:10,592
On this farm?
- Yes.

500
00:57:10,593 --> 00:57:13,593
Did you spend your youth here?
- I was born here, yes.

501
