504
00:57:31,781 --> 00:57:34,781
Costs were lower,
so we needed less money.

505
00:57:36,986 --> 00:57:39,986
But did people have a good life?

506
00:57:40,990 --> 00:57:43,990
You can't compare it.

507
00:57:45,395 --> 00:57:47,262
Life was very different.

508
00:57:47,263 --> 00:57:50,263
But was life better then
than it is now?

509
00:57:51,668 --> 00:57:54,668
Or is life better now?

510
00:57:54,704 --> 00:57:57,704
I suppose it is better now.

511
00:58:00,977 --> 00:58:03,977
Did life use to be too hard?
- Yes, it was indeed.

512
00:58:06,015 --> 00:58:09,015
It is better now,
but people have to leave their land.

513
00:58:10,753 --> 00:58:13,753
Yes, because...

514
00:58:14,557 --> 00:58:17,557
