it floats on the surface.

521
00:59:07,644 --> 00:59:10,644
Is it a good product?
- Well...

522
00:59:12,849 --> 00:59:15,450
it used to be a good product.

523
00:59:15,451 --> 00:59:18,451
Is it a question of competition?
- Yes, it must be.

524
00:59:20,690 --> 00:59:23,690
The demand may also have dropped.

525
00:59:26,462 --> 00:59:29,462
What is it used for?

526
00:59:30,934 --> 00:59:33,934
For perfumes.

527
00:59:35,305 --> 00:59:38,305
And soap?
- Yes, also for soap and suchlike.

528
01:00:18,681 --> 01:00:21,681
How did you meet your husband?

529
01:00:21,718 --> 01:00:24,718
I just did by accident.

530
01:00:24,988 --> 01:00:27,823
At a party?

531
01:00:27,824 --> 01:00:30,659
No, by accident.

532
01:00:30,660 --> 01:00:33,660
In a lane.

533
01:00:34,197 --> 01:00:37,132
And then?
- Well...

534
01:00:37,133 --> 01:00:39,701
we got to know each other
and then we got married.

535
01:00:39,702 --> 01:00:41,269
And it was successful?

536
01:00:41,270 --> 01:00:44,270
Yes, because I have been living here
for 27 years.

537
01:00:51,547 --> 01:00:54,547
Are people leaving the area?

538
01:00:55,418 --> 01:00:58,220
Yes, many are leaving.

539
01:00:58,221 --> 01:01:01,221
And what do you think about that?

540
01:01:02,625 --> 01:01:05,625
We take it as it comes.

541
01:01:06,996 --> 01:01:09,996
But it must affect you?

542
01:01:11,134 --> 01:01:14,134
Yes, it does a bit.

543
01:01:19,809 --> 01:01:22,809
But could you tell me...

544
01:01:23,246 --> 01:01:26,246
what the mountains mean to you?

545
01:01:26,816 --> 01:01:29,816
What do you think as you climb them?

546
01:01:31,888 --> 01:01:34,389
We have always lived here.

547
01:01:34,390 --> 01:01:37,390
We think about the children,
about family and friends...

548
01:01:39,896 --> 01:01:41,763
who have left for the city.

549
01:01:41,764 --> 01:01:44,764
But we have always lived here.
We don't want to leave yet.

550
01:01:48,137 --> 01:01:51,137
We have lived here.
And this is our life.

551
01:01:53,876 --> 01:01:56,876
Do you ever think about
how the world changes?

552
01:01:58,948 --> 01:02:01,948
Do you have any ideas about it?

553
01:02:02,652 --> 01:02:05,652
Yes, we think about it sometimes.

554
01:02:08,191 --> 01:02:11,191
What do you think, then?

555
01:02:11,194 --> 01:02:14,194
We wonder what it will be like
for those after us.

556
01:02:17,667 --> 01:02:20,667
Like unemployment, for instance?

557
01:02:21,370 --> 01:02:23,805
Yes, exactly.

558
01:02:23,806 --> 01:02:26,806
Because they talk about progress
and its advantages.

559
01:02:27,510 --> 01:02:30,510
But there are disadvantages too.

560
01:02:34,817 --> 01:02:37,817
Such as?

561
