577
01:10:02,398 --> 01:10:05,398
That's when we came back.

578
01:10:06,802 --> 01:10:09,802
We couldn't stay in Africa
any longer, because of the Party.

579
01:10:12,041 --> 01:10:15,041
My husband hadn't seen his relatives
in ten years.

580
01:10:15,978 --> 01:10:18,978
He wanted to see his village again.

581
01:10:20,683 --> 01:10:23,683
So in 1923...

582
01:10:24,853 --> 01:10:27,853
we came back to the area
of Reggio Emilia.

583
01:10:28,390 --> 01:10:31,025
And then you became Italian?

584
01:10:31,026 --> 01:10:34,026
No, I have always been Italian
since I was born.

585
01:10:37,900 --> 01:10:40,900
I was acknowledged straight away
by my father.

586
01:10:42,838 --> 01:10:45,838
It wasn't a fake acknowledgement...

587
01:10:47,309 --> 01:10:49,711
for payment.

588
01:10:49,712 --> 01:10:52,712
He personally went to register me
as his daughter...

589
01:10:55,317 --> 01:10:58,317
with a woman
he wasn't allowed to marry.

590
01:10:59,154 --> 01:11:02,154
They weren't permitted to marry.

591
01:11:03,759 --> 01:11:06,759
They just lived together,
my father and my mother.

592
01:11:07,963 --> 01:11:10,963
They had five children.

593
01:11:12,568 --> 01:11:15,568
Four boys and one girl: me.

594
01:11:15,638 --> 01:11:18,638
All with the Italian nationality?
- All of them.

595
01:11:21,143 --> 01:11:24,143
The boys all joined the army
to do their military service.

596
01:11:24,213 --> 01:11:26,881
In 1923...

597
01:11:26,882 --> 01:11:29,882
you couldn't go out
after nine o'clock in Italy.

598
01:11:30,886 --> 01:11:33,886
The fascist party had set a curfew.

599
01:11:38,160 --> 01:11:41,160
Voting was compulsory then.

600
01:11:43,666 --> 01:11:46,100
Everywhere it said:

601
01:11:46,101 --> 01:11:48,269
Vote!

602
01:11:48,270 --> 01:11:51,270
People who didn't vote
for the fascists didn't get jobs.

603
01:11:55,177 --> 01:11:58,112
I was coloured...

604
01:11:58,113 --> 01:12:01,113
so I always had a crowd
of children following me like flies.

605
01:12:03,752 --> 01:12:06,752
They shouted: 'Look, a black woman,
a Negress. Look at that!'

606
01:12:09,958 --> 01:12:12,958
What about his relatives?
- His parents were terrible.

607
01:12:14,563 --> 01:12:17,563
They didn't want to share a meal
with me...

608
01:12:18,434 --> 01:12:21,434
because I was black.

609
01:12:22,037 --> 01:12:24,739
In despair I said to him:

610
01:12:24,740 --> 01:12:27,740
Either you allow me to go back
or I jump in front of a train.

611
01:12:30,079 --> 01:12:32,113
The family suggested...

612
01:12:32,114 --> 01:12:35,114
I leave one of my daughters
with my husband...

613
01:12:36,685 --> 01:12:39,587
and that I take the other one
with me.

614
01:12:39,588 --> 01:12:42,588
The older one I'd be allowed to keep.

615
01:12:43,125 --> 01:12:46,125
She's not so black.
She's got black hair...

616
01:12:48,197 --> 01:12:51,197
and an olive skin.

617
01:12:52,267 --> 01:12:55,267
The other one had a white skin
and auburn hair.

618
01:12:57,539 --> 01:13:00,539
She was white
and she'd be for her father.

619
01:13:01,710 --> 01:13:04,710
So the whiter one would stay?
- Yes, with her father.

620
01:13:07,149 --> 01:13:10,149
And the dark one
would come to Africa.

621
01:13:18,527 --> 01:13:21,527
But I left for Africa
with my two girls.

622
01:13:24,800 --> 01:13:27,800
I said: I won't have anything to do
with those people.

623
01:13:29,438 --> 01:13:31,773
Give me my daughters...

624
01:13:31,774 --> 01:13:33,274
and I'll be off.

625
01:13:33,275 --> 01:13:36,077
And my husband let me go.

626
01:13:36,078 --> 01:13:38,079
After four months...

627
01:13:38,080 --> 01:13:41,080
I could buy a ticket
for my husband.

628
01:13:44,420 --> 01:13:47,420
He started work straight away.

629
01:13:47,823 --> 01:13:50,823
Who was in power at that time?

630
01:13:51,660 --> 01:13:54,660
Always the Italians.

631
01:13:55,164 --> 01:13:58,164
It was Italy. And Eritrea was...

632
01:14:00,269 --> 01:14:03,269
a dominion, a protectorate.

633
01:14:05,407 --> 01:14:08,407
At first it was better.

634
01:14:10,479 --> 01:14:13,479
There weren't so many differences.

635
01:14:14,216 --> 01:14:17,216
But later on we couldn't sit together
or eat together.

636
01:14:21,657 --> 01:14:23,758
We were always separate.

637
01:14:23,759 --> 01:14:26,327
Was that segregation by colour?
- Yes, colour.

638
01:14:26,328 --> 01:14:29,328
Apartheid?
- Yes, apartheid.

639
01:14:44,813 --> 01:14:47,813
