from the fascists...

643
01:15:07,870 --> 01:15:10,870
that was addressed to
Comrade Spaggiari.

644
01:15:12,007 --> 01:15:15,007
I said: 'My husband has never been
a comrade of yours.'

645
01:15:16,879 --> 01:15:19,879
'We'll see about that after the war',
they replied.

646
01:15:20,015 --> 01:15:23,015
'We don't know yet
who's going to win or lose.'

647
01:15:24,953 --> 01:15:27,953
God is great.

648
01:15:30,192 --> 01:15:33,192
Do you remember
the end of the Italian era?

649
01:15:34,796 --> 01:15:37,796
The end of the Italian period?

650
01:15:38,901 --> 01:15:41,901
They picked up all the Italians.

651
01:15:44,873 --> 01:15:47,873
They put them all together on lorries
whether they wanted to or not...

652
01:15:49,144 --> 01:15:51,746
and they shaved them bald.

653
01:15:51,747 --> 01:15:53,915
And they abused them terribly.

654
01:15:53,916 --> 01:15:56,916
Many of them died
and many of them escaped.

655
