And many of them got off
and ended up in Kenya.

656
01:16:09,197 --> 01:16:12,197
In Nairobi. In concentration camps.

657
01:16:15,237 --> 01:16:18,237
Were the English in power there then?

658
01:16:18,807 --> 01:16:21,807
Yes, the English.
What did the English do?

659
01:16:22,377 --> 01:16:25,377
The first thing they did was
to start plundering for food.

660
01:16:29,184 --> 01:16:32,184
And there was prostitution
everywhere.

661
01:16:33,121 --> 01:16:35,623
I even shook hands
with Haile Selassie.

662
01:16:35,624 --> 01:16:38,624
And then you returned to Italy?

663
01:16:39,261 --> 01:16:42,261
We had to leave in 1972.

664
01:16:43,966 --> 01:16:46,667
Or we could stay...

665
01:16:46,668 --> 01:16:49,668
at our own risk.

666
01:16:52,174 --> 01:16:55,174
But we had to leave.

667
01:16:55,611 --> 01:16:58,611
Because the Italians
were no longer in power.

668
01:16:59,581 --> 01:17:02,581
Eritrea had become...

669
01:17:03,018 --> 01:17:05,419
independent.

670
01:17:05,420 --> 01:17:07,555
We had become undesirables.

671
01:17:07,556 --> 01:17:10,556
