because we couldn't live without.

674
01:17:19,768 --> 01:17:22,768
And some pea flour.
That's really good.

675
01:17:23,739 --> 01:17:26,073
Only food.

676
01:17:26,074 --> 01:17:28,576
And some jewellery. Gold.

677
